He was releaved. He undressed her(so to speak) with his eyes.
"So who can I kill first?" He laughed.
He grabbed her, he was useing force, but he wasn't hurting her.
He began kissing her neck. He "explored" her with his hands. Every
curve, every sliver of metal. he was madely in love.
